What to Buy and Why: Series 1

Technology Documentary hosted by Cherry Healey, published by BBC in 2016 - English narration
  
http://docuwiki.net/images/6/6e/What-to-Buy-and-Why-Series-1-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------

What to Buy and Why
Cherry Healey enlists the help of top industry experts to get the inside track on the latest products, from cosmetics to clothing, technology to kitchen equipment.


2)  Part 2 
Cherry Heeley enlists the help of the UK's top professionals to work out which products we should be spending our money on. The elite groundsmen from English Heritage's most visited palace road test the latest gardening equipment. The programme also asks whether compact cameras should be ditched in favour of smart phones, and investigates whether travelling abroad to buy cosmetics could save money.
